HEADWORD: Filament
<hw>Fil"a*ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>filament</ets>, fr. L. <ets>filum</ets> thread. See <er>File</er> a
row.]</ety> <def>A thread or threadlike object or appendage; a
fiber;</def> <specif>esp.</specif> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>, <def>the
threadlike part of the stamen supporting the anther.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

